Text: Thanks for your participation in Deer Valley Jeff I want to say thank you so much for speaking at our Deer Valley Conference I know how difficult making and then keeping commitments like this can be You are a great great friend to have taken the time to help us out Hopefully it was helpful to you as well I thought this years conference was the best ever and the feedback we have already received supports that We had a fascinating mix of guests and panels and thanks to you it was a smash hit Deer Valley is our premier client event and you are a premier client Thank you for being generous with your time On behalf of all my partners we appreciate your friendship With kind personal regards Sincerely Jimmy
